This project involves an analysis of electric vehicle sales data across various states in India, divided into 2-wheeler and 4-wheeler segments. The analysis focuses on understanding the growth trends, identifying the top-performing makers and states, and estimating the revenue growth between 2022 and 2024. The primary goals were:

----Analyze the top and bottom makers in terms of 2-wheeler EV sales for the fiscal years 2023 and 2024.
----Identify the top 5 states with the highest EV penetration rates.
----Determine which states saw a decline in EV penetration from 2022 to 2024.
----Track quarterly sales trends for the top 5 makers of 4-wheelers.
----Compare EV sales and penetration rates between Delhi and Karnataka in 2024.
----Calculate the Compound Annual Growth Rate (CAGR) for the top makers and states.
----Identify the peak and low sales seasons and make future sales projections for 2030.
